    <string name="info">
        At First, thank you for using my App.

        \n\nWith this app you have an overview of your finances. You can add a new or change the actual profile in the main menu.
        There you can choose a empty or default profile. The default profile has some entries.

        \n\nIf you want to delete your profile, click on "Delete Profile" in the menu. If you want to duplicate your profile with all entries,
        click on "Duplicate Profile" in the menu.

        \n\nIn "Overview", you have a overview of the selected profile and you can change the profile name.

        \n\nIf you want to add a new income or change it, click on "Income" in the menu.

        \n\nIf you want to add a new expense or change it, click on "Expense" in the menu.

        \n\nIf you want to change the currency click on “Change Currency” in the menu,
